    "details": "Gld has been found vulnerable to multiple buffer overflows as\nwell as multiple format string vulnerabilities.\n\n> An attacker could exploit this vulnerability to execute\n> arbitrary code with the permissions of the user running Gld,\n> the default user being root.\n\nThe FreeBSD port defaults to running gld as the root user.\nThe risk of exploitation can be minimized by making gld\nlisten on the loopback address only, or configure it to only\naccept connections from trusted smtp servers.",
